intro.title: Welcome to Veloxx
intro.description: Veloxx is a lightning-fast, lightweight Rust library for in-memory data processing and analytics. It provides a modern, ergonomic API that competes with industry leaders like pandas and Polars while maintaining excellent performance and memory efficiency.

performance/benchmarks.title: Performance Benchmarks
performance/benchmarks.description: Veloxx is designed for maximum performance while maintaining a minimal footprint. Here are comprehensive benchmarks comparing Veloxx against industry-leading data processing libraries.

tutorials/customer_purchase_analysis.description: This tutorial demonstrates a more advanced workflow with the Veloxx library, including reading data from multiple CSV files, joining DataFrames, and performing a group-by aggregation.

tutorials/general_tutorial.description: This tutorial provides a quick tour of the Veloxx library, covering the basics of creating DataFrames, performing common data manipulation tasks, and using the library's more advanced features.
